data.description: *Home has an assumable VA loan. This charmer is going to knock you right off your feet! It is the epitome of southern charm and modern elegance. Step into a world of comfort and luxury as you explore the meticulously designed interior. The open-concept living area boasts an abundance of natural light that highlights the exquisite details like the exposed wood beams and exposed ductwork. This home also has industrial barn style second story loft w/ metal railing & wood ladder that can be seen from the downstairs living area. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, quartz countertops, custom maplewood cabinetry that has soft close doors & drawers & is wired for cabinet lighting.
